				\begin{document}$${\rm{CI}}=100\times [0.8\times \frac{{\rm{Fu}}2}{3.2\times {\rm{Ba}}1+0.8\times {\rm{Fu}}2}]$$\end{document}CI=100×[0.8×Fu23.2×Ba1+0.8×Fu2]with 0.8 and 3.2 representing enrichment weightings for Fu2 and Ba1 nematodes57. The Structure Index (SI) provides information about the complexity of the soil food web. A highly structured food web with a high SI suggests ecosystem stability, while low values imply environmental disturbance57.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
